   <S PAR='17' RSNT='1' SNO='17'>HOW TO USE THE LIFE-STUDY MESSAGES</S>
   <S PAR='18' RSNT='1' SNO='18'>During the last two or three years I have been very much concerned as to how we can use all the groceries of the Life-study Messages.</S>
