   <S PAR='20' RSNT='1' SNO='20'>Although this way of getting into the Life-studies works to a certain extent, it is not the best way.</S>
   <S PAR='21' RSNT='1' SNO='21'>The best way is not to go through a book of the Bible verse by verse or to read the Life-study Message from the first line to the last line.</S>
   <S PAR='22' RSNT='1' SNO='22'>The best way is to pick out the crucial points and to get into these crucial points.</S>
   <S PAR='23' RSNT='1' SNO='23'>If you felt burdened from the Lord to study the book of 1 Corinthians the Lord might lead you to begin by picking up one crucial point in chapter one.</S>
