   <S PAR='75' RSNT='1' SNO='75'>You may decide to pick up just one crucial point in each chapter of 1 Corinthians.</S>
   <S PAR='76' RSNT='1' SNO='76'>When you get through 1 Corinthians, even though you did not read it verse by verse and you did not read all the Life-studies line by line, you will have acquired a bird s-eye-view of this book, and this book will have been deposited into your being.</S>
