   <S PAR='81' RSNT='1' SNO='81'>In like manner, we all have the divine groceries of the Life-study Messages, but we all need to be trained to cook them.</S>
   <S PAR='82' RSNT='1' SNO='82'>The Lord has given us the Holy Bible, the Word, and His Holy Spirit always goes along with the Bible.</S>
